383
00:28:53,093 --> 00:28:54,123
Mr. Baek.

384
00:28:56,523 --> 00:28:59,793
There's something I'd like to ask you. It may sound impolite,

385
00:29:00,693 --> 00:29:02,693
but I need to ask you just in case.

386
00:29:03,263 --> 00:29:04,963
Please don't get any wrong ideas.

387
00:29:06,463 --> 00:29:07,493
Go ahead.

388
00:29:08,493 --> 00:29:11,163
Did something happen while you were...

389
00:29:11,823 --> 00:29:13,223
mentoring Se Ju?

390
00:29:16,363 --> 00:29:19,093
Your wife is going around my back to influence the media and investors.

391
00:29:19,093 --> 00:29:21,423
I want to know why she's so out to get him.

392
00:29:22,123 --> 00:29:26,123
I let it slide because I didn't want to disgrace your name in any way,

393
00:29:26,393 --> 00:29:30,463
