397
00:29:47,263 --> 00:29:49,663
I thought it'd be more lucrative than collecting paintings.

398
00:29:50,823 --> 00:29:52,623
I don't know why you're getting so worked up about it.

399
00:29:53,763 --> 00:29:56,823
You see, I know you very well.

400
00:29:57,963 --> 00:30:01,123
You're doing it to suffocate him because he's stopped writing.

401
00:30:03,723 --> 00:30:05,723
