407
00:30:27,723 --> 00:30:31,293
Please. Please stop now.

408
00:30:31,893 --> 00:30:35,763
Tae Min and I are the ones who need to get down on our knees, not Se Ju.

409
00:30:36,123 --> 00:30:38,023
What are you talking about?

410
00:30:38,123 --> 00:30:40,923
Do you know what Tae Min and I have done...

411
00:30:40,923 --> 00:30:42,323
to Se Ju 10 years ago?

412
00:30:42,893 --> 00:30:44,623
Do you have any idea...

413
00:30:45,023 --> 00:30:47,963
who made Tae Min a professor as a writer?

414
00:30:49,293 --> 00:30:50,763
Who made him a professor?

415
00:30:52,763 --> 00:30:53,993
What does that mean?

416
00:30:54,763 --> 00:30:55,823
Are you saying...

417
00:30:56,523 --> 00:31:00,863
Tae Min stole what Se Ju wrote or what?

418
00:31:05,593 --> 00:31:06,623
No way.

419
00:31:07,923 --> 00:31:08,963
Is that true?

420
00:31:12,023 --> 00:31:13,123
Then...

421
00:31:14,163 --> 00:31:16,523
you should do something about it.

422
00:31:19,063 --> 00:31:20,063
Shouldn't you?

423
00:31:23,163 --> 00:31:24,893
- Thank you. - Thank you.

424
00:31:28,223 --> 00:31:29,423
- Thank you. - Bye.

